-- European Stocks Advance; BG Group, Danske Bank, Hermes International Climb
-- B y   W i l l   H a d f i e l d
-- 2010-11-02T11:36:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-02/european-stocks-fluctuate-bg-group-bp-advance-as-bbva-assa-abloy-slide.html
European stocks advanced, as gains by
Danske Bank A/S and Hermes International outweighed declines by
Bwin Interactive Entertainment AG and Serco Group Plc.  The benchmark Stoxx Europe 600 Index increased 0.4 percent
to 267.53 at 11:35 a.m. in London, after earlier swinging
between gains and losses at least nine times.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
